OL,3,CMP says children's safety online is
OL,4,C'most defining issue of our time'
OL,6,FSpeaking in Westminster Hall on
OL,7,FTuesday (26 November), the Labour MP
OL,8,Fsaid: "The children in my town have
OL,9,Ftold me that age verification
OL,10,Frequirements are easily passed through
OL,11,Fand that content on these sites are
OL,12,Fdeeply disturbing. So we need to talk
OL,13,Fabout stopping those sites or changing
OL,14,Fthe age verification."
OL,16,FIt comes as new legislation, the
OL,17,FOnline Safety Act, sets out to
OL,18,Fminimise risks, placing new legal
OL,19,Fresponsibilities on online providers
OL,20,Fto keep young people safe.
