OL,3,CMP says children's safety online is
OL,4,C'most defining issue of our time'
OL,6,FResearch by regulator Ofcom shows
OL,7,Faround 70% of parents are worried
OL,8,Fabout their children being bullied
OL,9,Fonline.
OL,11,FMs McEvoy has been working with
OL,12,Fschools and parents in her
OL,13,Fconstituency to improve online safety.
OL,14,FShe has been horrified at some of the
OL,15,Fthings young people have been exposed
OL,16,Fto while using apps.
OL,18,FTeachers and pupils at one school in
OL,19,FDarlington agree with Ms McEvoy that
OL,20,Fmore needs to be done.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
