OL,3,CMP says children's safety online is
OL,4,C'most defining issue of our time'
OL,6,FGemma Elysee, deputy principal and
OL,7,Fsafeguarding lead at Beaumont Academy,
OL,8,Fsaid: "There are far too many risks
OL,9,Fonline for our young people, and there
OL,10,Fare insufficient measures in place to
OL,11,Fprotect our young people from
OL,12,Faccessing the most dangerous parts of
OL,13,Fthe internet.
OL,15,F"In school, we have a lot of measures
OL,16,Fin place, filtering and monitoring, so
OL,17,Fwhen they're online in our school
OL,18,Fbuilding they're exceptionally safe.
OL,19,FHowever, that doesn't always extend to
OL,20,Fwhen they leave the school building
OL,21,Fand go into the community."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
