OL,3,CMP says children's safety online is
OL,4,C'most defining issue of our time'
OL,6,FNathan Barrowcliff, a pupil at
OL,7,FBarrowcliff Academy, said: "Kids
OL,8,Fonline are getting exposed to this
OL,9,Fstuff, and companies aren't doing
OL,10,Fanything about it.
OL,12,F"I get that people say it's a breach
OL,13,Fof privacy, but if nothing's in place
OL,14,Fyet, us kids, the next generation,
OL,15,Fwill be affected by mental health
OL,16,Fproblems."
